README.md
     1→# The only accessible & unstyled & full featured Input OTP component in the Web.
     2→
     3→### OTP Input for React 🔐 by [@guilhermerodz](https://twitter.com/guilherme_rodz)
     4→
     5→<h3 align="center">Hero Sponsors 🎖️</h3>
     6→<p align="center">
     7→<a href="https://go.clerk.com/input-otp" target="_blank">
     8→<img alt="Clerk" src='https://input-otp.rodz.dev/sponsors/clerk-wordmark-white-in-black-bg.svg' width="130" style="aspect-ratio: auto;"/>
     9→</a>
    10→<a href="https://go.resend.com/input-otp" target="_blank">
    11→<img alt="Resend" src='https://input-otp.rodz.dev/sponsors/resend-wordmark-white-in-black-bg.svg' width="130" style="aspect-ratio: auto;"/>
    12→</a>
    13→<a href="https://evomi.com/?utm_source=github&utm_campaign=otp" target="_blank">
    14→<img alt="Evomi" src='https://input-otp.rodz.dev/sponsors/evomi-wordmark-white-in-black-bg.svg' width="130" style="aspect-ratio: auto;"/>
    15→</a>
    16→</p>
