   523→
   524→<details>
   525→<summary>[DX] Add Tailwind autocomplete for `containerClassname` attribute in VS Code.</summary>
   526→
   527→Add the following setting to your `.vscode/settings.json`:
   528→```diff
   529→{
   530→  "tailwindCSS.classAttributes": [
   531→    "class",
   532→    "className",
   533→+   ".*ClassName"
   534→  ]
   535→}
   536→```
   537→</details>
